  "remarks": "Karina Ramzanovna Kadyrova is the daughter of Ramzan Kadyrov, President Vladimir Putin’s key Chechen ally. She has been appointed as the Head of Pre-School education of Grozny due to her close relations to her father Ramzan Kadyrov. She is therefore associated with Ramzan Kadyrov, President of the Republic of Chechnya.",
